title: #92Noon Live from TCO: Boudreau / Burns / Miller / Birk / Tice
description:
The FAN's Paul Allen and Eric Nordquist are live at TCO Studios from the TCO Performance Center in Eagan!

They open the show recapping last night's Wild loss to the Sharks with head coach Bruce Boudreau, Nordo introduces the No More L's "Noel" cover, and plenty of football talk the rest of the way with Dan Miller, Ryan Burns, Matt Birk, and Mike Tice.
